.SH NAME
submit_bio_wait \- submit a bio, and wait until it completes
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" submit_bio_wait
.BI "(struct bio *bio "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bio" 12
The \fIstruct bio\fP which describes the I/O
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Simple wrapper around \fBsubmit_bio\fP. Returns 0 on success, or the error from
\fBbio_endio\fP on failure.

WARNING: Unlike to how \fBsubmit_bio\fP is usually used, this function does not
result in bio reference to be consumed. The caller must drop the reference
on his own.
